name: Adundance
description:
***Gold Standard Edition*** 
This is the 1/1 Gold Standard Edition only available from my side of the collab. This song is also available on the Artikude page as a 63/63 making 64 total editions available. 

I present to you stunning visuals combined with amazing sounds in hopes of creating the new NFT Music standard.
This collaboration represents the infinite potential we all have to create abundance together. Thank you for the help of @artikudee @grant4uatro and @mastersantoro

Produced by Grant Fore
Written, Recorded and Performed by me
Mixed by Santoro
Cover Art Gif by Artikude
